{
  "stem": "20800.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they ask us for documents, we said we lost them all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the bomb was, and things like this, we lost them all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When these people start to decide that all Jews have to go in this place, and they sent one person from-- from the town to ask us whether we're Jews.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we said we're not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they wanted documents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, we haven't got documents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All documents is we lost.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, you have to-- to have documents because there was probably somebody pointed to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he said, if you don't produce the documents you have to go down there, in this [NON-ENGLISH] where all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's where it started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I, of course--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew that they will go-- that-- you see, in Russia we didn't have any ghettos like here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You stay here and you work there, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put them all in one place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every night the truck comes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put the people on the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They went, and we never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- make the Jews to make the graves for themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they're all gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I said, I'm going to get documents, and we're not going to this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he gave me three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I did, I left my mother [SOBBING] and sister down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went by myself to Krasnodar, where we start, where I had my friends from university.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we left all those-- all our things, our possessions from our flat where I lived, to one family, which lived not far away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The grand piano and everything, they took it to their place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I did, I even ask, we didn't look like-- I didn't look much like Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
